sequenceDiagram
    participant Timer as Refresh Tick / Key r
    participant Model as Bubble Tea Model
    participant Client as internal/tui.Client
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Store as marketdata.Store
    participant Render as Lip Gloss Renderer

    Timer->>Model: tickMsg or key message
    Model->>Client: Snapshot(ctx)
    Client->>API: GET /api/v1/snapshot + X-API-Key
    API->>Store: Snapshot()
    Store-->>API: marketdata.Snapshot
    API-->>Client: JSON response
    Client-->>Model: snapshotMsg
    Model->>Model: update state, selection, latency
    Model->>Render: View()
    Render-->>Model: terminal string
